%% Diagram: Gossip Membership - 3-Phase Exchange + Phi Accrual Convict Path
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Node A (initiator)
    participant B as Node B (random peer)
    participant C as Node C (3rd party)

    Note over A: every ~1s: pick random live peer
    A->>B: SYN(digest of known endpoints + versions)
    B-->>A: ACK(diff: entries B has newer + digest of what B wants)
    A->>B: ACK2(entries A has newer)

    Note over A,B: each merges by max(version) per (endpoint, app-state-key)<br/>O(log N) rounds to fully propagate

    Note over A: per-peer phi accrual:<br/>track inter-heartbeat distribution<br/>phi(t) = -log10(1 - F(t - t_last))<br/>if phi(C) > 8 -> mark C suspect/convicted
    A->>B: gossip "C is DOWN, gen=g, version=v"
    B-->>A: merged - if newer B propagates further
